{"tid":319760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"隱適美箍牙日記","createTime":"2017-07-13T04:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T13:59:33.000Z","uid":14636,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c305a89938033598f068754ad90105142f52a66","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:48:28.000Z","msg":"今日第一日，係有啲啲緊<br />\n但又唔算好痛 <br />\n<br />\n頭先除左落黎食譚仔完全無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過一帶番個下就痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申非打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5506885efa55126a7d9ce231d20c07fc425c38a","tid":319760,"uid":20640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"幾錢箍幾耐"},{"pid":"de97981f48cfcf4608c4e933cf9382759cb2f6f0","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢箍幾耐</blockquote><br />\n45000<br />\n預2年"},{"pid":"30a362107ef634bccd7f0743534e423e083c2424","tid":319760,"uid":10889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edcd0dc7fc56b08fffbee74141f350b5584b62e","tid":319760,"uid":80953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:54:13.000Z","msg":"你本身啲牙唔算好歪?<br />\n聽唔少隱適美用家話會帶得好痺好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecda5f31acd17d65ef66f830537dfd4f0d5f0a6","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:55:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你本身啲牙唔算好歪?<br />\n聽唔少隱適美用家話會帶得好痺好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class