id":"5b76d887caf7dbf21280f58bfde637d416ff18ce","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係隱適美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n箍咗一年都冇<br />\n34000</blockquote><br />\n得一年，其實啲牙本身都唔差"},{"pid":"c2a82ed388920cb5321284ea8f46ae5cdc06359f","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係隱適美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n箍咗一年都冇<br />\n34000</blockquote><br />\n得一年，其實啲牙本身都唔差</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbf151e6d8543511fd68eaec62705c8fc4b9cad","tid":319760,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:06:31.000Z","msg":"你地係去邊間箍架?<br />\n係咪上隱適美求其揀一間就得<br />\n價錢會唔會好大分別??<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7b737b1581437a63be8f8ab2cc5639704f7398","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地係去邊間箍架?<br />\n係咪上隱適美求其揀一間就得<br />\n價錢會唔會好大分別??<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係朋友介紹<br />\n話計平啲<br />\n但其實都好似差唔多，另外有個fd都係呢個價"},{"pid":"e90b7574c397a9847467bdabaeddc2878c71874b","tid":319760,"uid":6308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係隱適美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n箍咗一年都冇<br />\n34000</blockquote><br />\n得一年，其實啲牙本身都唔差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係 我之前啲牙真係好核突<br />\n又爆牙 啲牙又前後前後咁生<br />\n但係唔知點解我咁快搞掂"},{"pid":"bace49c0fe1499a3c25ad34bfcf8c475233faca4","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係隱適美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n箍咗一年都冇<br />\n34000</blockquote><br />\n得一年，其實啲牙本身都唔差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係 我之前啲牙真係好核突<br />\n又爆牙 啲牙又前後前後咁生<br />\n但係唔知點解我咁快搞掂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 幾歲"},{"pid":"e468a2f3ddf9ae40318b3b721fc0490f1e981c45","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"帶左半日<br />\n依家食飯，牙軟軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530fd8c541b35b15b9d30447d7127b0bf2c9f0fd","tid":319760,"uid":128198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係隱適美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n箍咗一年都冇<br />\n34000</blockquote><br />\n得一年，其實啲牙本身都唔差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係 我之前啲牙真係好核突<br />\n又爆牙 啲牙又前後前後咁生<br />\n但係唔知點解我咁快搞掂</blockquote><br />\n箍一年應該唔洗剝牙，同本身只係有少少唔齊<br />\n如果唔係既話.. 又咁快箍完.. 小心牙腳郁得太快牙根會死"},{"pid":"d0739851b0c1dbedc8ead357e7a714fa2031fd64","tid":319760,"uid":128198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地係去邊間箍架?<br />\n係咪上隱適美求其揀一間就得<br />\n價錢會唔會好大分別??<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實依家好多牙醫都有做，你揀幾間有free consult既去比佢睇下，有揀一間做"},{"pid":"7ed97639408d90740200def70cc0bb3392406b16","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"依家照鏡唔知心理作用定咩<br />\n啲牙好似即刻黃左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咪要每餐都刷牙嫁<br />\n定夜晚刷就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850341cefbd2df74ee815d63a7fdef26eb87b088","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"個牙套𠝹到條脷損左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a150f61d24ad4f25c67cbb196190121f2d4a6fb3","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T22:45:30.000Z","msg":"Day 2 <br />\n開始黎料，除左再帶返箍個下痛到喊<br />\n食野牙軟軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2669bad3a2fa56ef6c651fcf18ad79afd9fdbc9","tid":319760,"uid":7697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T22:54:38.000Z","msg":"食野要除 食完要上返套？"},{"pid":"a8d33c09c94be0557d7a957dc62abc502d1d8238","tid":319760,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:03:27.000Z","msg":"個人箍完後有以下感想：<br />\n1. 帶再咁上下好易會偷懶，覺得唔洗時時戴都可以轉下一個箍<br />\n2. 係會好易牙黃，難keep住衛生<br />\n3. 透明箍無想像咁靚，因為都會每到面腫"},{"pid":"6523e9b9c1868f258ec3ff8de36094e3cc9110f7","tid":319760,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食野要除 食完要上返套？</blockquote><br />\nyes"},{"pid":"a42c20f8ecae69192a24b11abb9ce40e0fe0aab7","tid":319760,"uid":112317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:25:03.000Z","msg":"我都箍緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2星期換1個牙套，每次一換完之後個2，3日會痛 食野都要慢慢咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506abeadd7bc61ab0d65d2921713cdb33af49ab1","tid":319760,"uid":48738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:42:17.000Z","msg":"等緊上箍 好淆底添<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa7630aac03729193b66ae0ebd16362259c49c9","tid":319760,"uid":43045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:57:22.000Z","msg":"我都cool緊, 已經一年, 習慣哂開始無感覺<br />\n<br />\n我係一星期換一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e928faccd5e6e6958e38729c5075bb545b79b66","tid":319760,"uid":3685,"lik