戴緊retainer 但懶到成個禮拜無戴</blockquote><br />\n無帶兩日retainer已經feel到走哂位</blockquote><br />\n一戴番果種痛真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慘過戴新箍</blockquote><br />\n其實覺得retainer無乜力可以點搞"},{"pid":"a06d7dff9ed27ee7446258cf24caa2d6b56819e2","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:14:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得最痛係除完再帶個下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01ca82159e4817fc104dad76461fd1f35955a72","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人箍完後有以下感想：<br />\n1. 帶再咁上下好易會偷懶，覺得唔洗時時戴都可以轉下一個箍<br />\n2. 係會好易牙黃，難keep住衛生<br />\n3. 透明箍無想像咁靚，因為都會每到面腫</blockquote><br />\n我外表上唔係好睇得出喎"},{"pid":"f432a7b302d5f77e68c14820e9d96ea745c7d46d","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:17:27.000Z","msg":"係會keep住講野痴脷根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158490d58e2878920283b46538171fbd1e1c864a","tid":319760,"uid":57204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新箍頭幾日唔好食啲易上色野，會好快黃<br />\n千祈唔好戴住佢飲野（除咗水）<br />\n買盒牙線棒，餐餐清牙罅<br />\n刷牙刷埋個箍，唔係會好臭<br />\n<br />\n利申箍完戴緊retainer 但懶到成個禮拜無戴</blockquote><br />\n無帶兩日retainer已經feel到走哂位</blockquote><br />\n一戴番果種痛真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慘過戴新箍</blockquote><br />\n其實覺得retainer無乜力可以點搞</blockquote><br />\n一係就係你啲牙已經無點走位，所以無咗果種掹住嘅感覺<br />\n一係就係你啲牙神力搞到個箍鬆哂<br />\n換過一個戴<br />\n<br />\n正常佢會比幾個你做後備，訓覺先戴唔會太污糟<br />\n一個應該可以戴到大半年嘅"},{"pid":"c8ec66fe08987d2158e201f4a4bea3945ba96b8d","tid":319760,"uid":57204,"like":0,"dislike"