美個大會，果到d專家話一星期一次都無問題，自此我就一星期一個<br />\n<br />\n利申 我個牙醫診所係隱適美既加盟店（好似係）"},{"pid":"a3ad05e4c0ac2fce701cd24bbc07f82221c20576","tid":319760,"uid":48738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由第一次諮詢, 直到戴上第一個箍, 中間隔咗幾耐時間?</blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf8e638fd061d9aa4a9cd9953faa7bcfb807fa4","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由第一次諮詢, 直到戴上第一個箍, 中間隔咗幾耐時間?</blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n總共一個月<br />\n<br />\n第一次就倒模，send 資料去外國<br />\n<br />\n第二次就兩星期後，睇報告（預計點箍/簽consent確認你同意箍/.......）<br />\n<br />\n再兩星期後真上箍"},{"pid":"ca2047e2679be28a072368d91935a280c097a961","tid":319760,"uid":84967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"我要箍3年<br />\n$36000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3442fd754a4e12406d51646acf870f9c815ed00","tid":319760,"uid":128198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由第一次諮詢, 直到戴上第一個箍, 中間隔咗幾耐時間?</blockquote><br />\n我6星期倒，但見過有巴絲話搵好出名個d成幾個月都未有"},{"pid":"abd73b37a9b796d2328de32b8ddf4fd3c8c452a7","tid":319760,"uid":84967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我要箍3年<br />\n$36000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbtw 就黎箍左2年了"},{"pid":"8b361785d56ed5d9bea0d09e3a6b0ae69d42b1c3","tid":319760,"uid":72891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"箍牙箍年半<br />\nTotal 32000"},{"pid":"58a49bf9888129e350f575558e42033de0763f6c","tid":319760,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T18:00:05.000Z","msg":"好想快啲完<br />\n依家先第三日<img src=\"